{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/img_gp_en.png?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/img_girls.png?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Black Fairy Tale is a game that enhances abilities and features automatic combat.\uff08Gameplay imitates and learns keyboard warriors\uff09</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deceived Little Red Riding Hood, vengeful Yuriosa, righteous female Taoist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose a girl and walk through a forest full of monsters, only through battle can you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each time you defeat an enemy, you can choose a card that will have different ways of strengthening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/gif_select.gif?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/img_build_en.png?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast paced and easy placement battles, equipped with a variety of weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A shield that combines offense and defense, a potion that restores life, and a gemstone that constantly appreciates in value</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/gif_battle.gif?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are a wide variety of genres to choose from, with different experiences in each battle, and various artifacts to assist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/gif_atlas.gif?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every girl has her own unique trick, which may change the core of your construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/gif_skill.gif?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The crisis ridden forest is also full of opportunities, who wouldn't want to be intimate with the succubus boss?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/img_shop.jpg?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/img_story_en.png?t=1737514580\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every girl in a fairy tale has a tragic past, and their future will be rewritten by you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Mainly because the development was rushed and there was no time to do the plot)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/extras/gif_cool.gif?t=1737514580\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737514580","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/page.bg.jpg?t=1737514580","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/8aaa6661a3bcde2ea870af8892d47f4dae27782c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737514580","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437060/8aaa6661a3bcde2ea870af8892d47f4dae27782c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737514580","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" s